locality: Loja: Just before bridge before Yangana, ca 100 m above road on steep slope.
Caracas between Vilcabamba and Yangana. Riverside vegetation.
Road San Pedro de la Bendita (W of Catamayo)-El Cisne, c. km 8. Northern extension of the Catamayo valley.
Road La Toma (Catamayo) - Loja, about km 5 from La Toma. Semi-arid mountain forest.
Pampas de Hospital, entre el cruce al puesto de vigilancia Cabo Cotrina y El Caucho.
